OL,3,CThieves trash hospice counselling
OL,4,Crooms in early hours raid
OL,6,FStaff at a hospice say they were left
OL,7,Fin "shock" after thieves stole
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds worth of items
OL,9,Fduring an early hours break-in.
OL,11,FThe burglars smashed windows to get
OL,12,Finto Overgate Hospice in Elland,
OL,13,FHalifax, at around 4am on Sunday 5
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FAfter breaking into one of the
OL,17,Fbuildings, they forced their way into
OL,18,Fcounselling pods used by bereaved
OL,19,Frelatives. Windows were smashed and
OL,20,Fitems left strewn across rooms.
