OL,3,CThieves trash hospice counselling
OL,4,Crooms in early hours raid
OL,6,F"There's nothing that can excuse this
OL,7,Fawful crime and the emotional impact
OL,8,Fit has on our patients, staff and
OL,9,Fvolunteers.
OL,11,F"Some of our patients are currently
OL,12,Freceiving end of life care and for the
OL,13,Fnursing team to be taken away from
OL,14,Fproviding that care in order to think
OL,15,Fof ways to protect them and contact
OL,16,Fthe police is just not acceptable."
