OL,4,Crooms in early hours raid
OL,6,FThe break-in comes at the start of a
OL,7,Fyear when the hospice begin work on a
OL,8,Fbrand new #12.75m development to
OL,9,Fincrease the number of people they can
OL,10,Fsupport with end of life care.
OL,12,FIn a Facebook post, the hospice said:
OL,13,F"We can't put into words how scared
OL,14,Four staff were as they watched the
OL,15,Fchaos unfold before their eyes, but we
OL,16,Fare so proud of their bravery and
OL,17,Fdedication to those in our care.
