OL,3,CThieves trash hospice counselling
OL,4,Crooms in early hours raid
OL,6,F"We are devastated by the damage
OL,7,Fcaused to these beautiful spaces, not
OL,8,Fto mention the feeling of safety our
OL,9,Fstaff and patients deserve."
OL,11,FCounselling services were disrupted by
OL,12,Fthe break-in, but the care for hospice
OL,13,Fpatients was not affected.
OL,15,FAnyone with information is being asked
OL,16,Fto contact the police.
